{"tid":1667984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新文宣方向 求下你地入嚟睇咗佢","createTime":"2019-10-21T17:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:13:33.000Z","uid":232728,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00c3b774159626ea49e091522c4b02d0066e64a6","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"11月24號係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">區議會選舉</span></strong>嘅日子。<br />\n雖然唔知政府會唔會改期，但係區議會選舉其實都係一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">非常重要嘅本土戰場</span></strong>，所以希望各位手足都抽啲時間睇呢篇文。如果真係唔想睇就碌到底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正如上面所講，<span style=\"color: red;\">淨番1個月多啲</span>就到區議會選舉，我地要好好利用呢1個月去幫自己打贏呢條戰線。小弟希望咁多位手足係呢1個月可以撥出小小時間一齊做<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選舉文宣</strong></span>。<br />\n小弟認為選舉文宣可以分成兩大類：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 推廣民主派</strong></span></span><br />\n希望咁多位手足可以宣傳下自己嗰區有邊啲<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主派候選人</strong></span>。<br />\n如果嗰候選人有番咁上下資歷，可能做緊<span style=\"color: red;\">社區主任</span>或者<span style=\"color: red;\">做過議員</span>又或者<span style=\"color: red;\">做緊議員</span>嘅，就講下佢地嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政績</strong></span>、為嗰社區做過啲咩等等。如果唔係嘅，可能係<span style=\"color: red;\">新人</span>嚟嘅，就盡量幫佢地宣傳下，講下佢地嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">背景</span>呀，講下<span style=\"color: red;\">有邊個幫佢地站台</span>等等。如果有為當區做過嘢嘅，就當然要寫出嚟啦~~<br />\n不過如果遇到一啲獨立候選人就一定一定要check清楚，大家都知有唔少聲稱獨立嘅人其實係建制派嚟，當然亦有民主派架喇，唔好冤枉好人就得！<br />\n小弟不才，冇乜藝術細胞，只可以提供啲資料同內容大綱比大家。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2F&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=f0f4e1a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/</a></span><br />\n呢嗰網有各選區嘅候選人亦都有清楚列明係建制派定民主派。如果咁多位手足有更好嘅網，歡迎開心share~~~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LaPgb49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLaPgb49.jpg&h=944e05ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，由於小弟南區人就用番南區做例子，呢嗰po就係一個好示範，share自己嗰區嘅民主派候選人比更多人睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 建制派政績</span></span></strong><br />\n除咗要宣傳自己友，都要幫對家宣傳下嘅。可以提番身邊啲街坊<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對家係任期內做咗啲咩好事</span></strong>。比啲例子大家：<br />\n<br />\n例子1. 香港仔區議員任葆琳小姐有一個傳說，就係係任期內<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只見過任小姐1-3次</span></strong>，其餘時間就唔知去咗邊。公平啲講句，任小姐都有政績嘅，分別係成功係香港仔爭取更多圍欄，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成功阻礙區內居民過馬路</strong></span>、成功趕走巴士線，比晒自己友進智公交啲小巴做啦，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成功爭取區內居民交通費上升</span></strong>咁囉、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成功爭取監控鏡頭</span></strong>，話要打擊亂抛垃圾喎。大家就可以宣傳對家嘅政績比其他街坊知。<br />\n<br />\n例子2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPPG7Hh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPPG7Hh.jpg&h=a91e6d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對家唔開會搞到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民生議題討論唔到</strong></span>，唔知班街坊點諗喇<br />\n<br />\n例子3.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hr6znX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hr6znX.jpg&h=ff693f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撐送中引發呢場運動</span></strong>，最後收唔到科，又唔知班街坊點諗。<br />\n<br />\n以上就係選舉文宣兩大方向，希望大家可以幫手做呢啲文宣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>share上去social media</strong></span>, fb ,ig , twitter都要見到。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">善用Hashtag</span></strong>：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#一票不投建制派</span></strong><br />\n英文嘅話，小弟暫時淨係諗到 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#SayNoToProBeijingCamp</span></strong> <br />\n希望有手足諗到嗰好啲嘅hashtag再share上嚟。<br />\n除咗social media，希望當區嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆或者深藍區嘅牆上</span></strong>都會見到，比多啲人知，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">突破同溫層</span></strong>。不過，希望手足係深藍區做文宣嘅時候，一定一定要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">注意安全</span></strong>，唔希望再有手足因為派文宣或者貼文宣而受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTLDR 懶人包: 做選舉文宣呀，推廣民主派同宣傳建制派做過嘅「好事」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港人 反抗！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"36c4eb8a437135330abfe40f485f6b24fa30d89d","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"cc2b41045437ce19a63f30f381517080d6e08b1c","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:59:19.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f845d02509b5bb6dffab27a22b4e594177d365df","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:59:29.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"b9078dd27bc005d623f1d1ea957415aec5499b3b","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:59:39.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"6cdecfa4265d4cc76b6d30cb12d97e4730ae262e","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"2c1d6905190814d1b08089824e72477ad23dedf1","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"195dd72a61bba8198a0c815ca4677f8e1a321705","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:00:19.000Z","msg":"深夜開po 冇人睇"},{"pid":"9e61ed61f3e613ed512aa81d0de9f0cc0498798c","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:00:33.000Z","msg":"搵人斷我啦 幫我推呀"},{"pid":"9ddc7b8eb73e59347197361708856aca3607e722","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"7/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a887e4c8bcaf3812edd221406361337e28e950d0","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:00:53.000Z","msg":"8/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501ee4c9e7d33341d346bf13c71f0e5cce80e954","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:01:04.000Z","msg":"9/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c08848e2c4b4c6197da514c768b0079c76d71e","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:01:14.000Z","msg":"10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e952b306a52ab07f90bc16d737fa18f2b9f18dfa","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"太夜開po 真係冇人睇"},{"pid":"436e1561170f44eee0784c30526c86a96d2e164d","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:01:44.000Z","msg":"得我自high"},{"pid":"dfa70c81194d4dce0d0648b633a3567b3c7a15e5","tid":1667984,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"太夜開po冇人睇<br />\nP牌幫你唔到"},{"pid":"abbb7878039f9ec764821fc665a0890241c6820a","tid":1667984,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:03:47.000Z","msg":"深夜係五毛時間，聽朝再開過試下啦"},{"pid":"282c9156d99ee109ebd21d791a5f6062e56c7641","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa70c81194d4dce0d0648b633a3567b3c7a15e5","tid":1667984,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"太夜開po冇人睇<br />\nP牌幫你唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:03:58.000Z","msg":"都多謝你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67256e5afbecd683215ed702459b54ab6e9990e0","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abbb7878039f9ec764821fc665a0890241c6820a","tid":1667984,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:03:47.000Z","msg":"深夜係五毛時間，聽朝再開過試下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:04:12.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160fbeb6988de1ed5d430493907f4f481e4e3e7e","tid":1667984,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:17:32.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"c02f1994306df2445e6f7e74b9ea1c1e937e53ca","tid":1667984,"uid":311563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:12:09.000Z","msg":"P牌象徵式推<br />\n<br />\n可能太夜啦，大家都訓哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a609893b71dded828ef0338398d770527848d5","tid":1667984,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"282c9156d99ee109ebd21d791a5f6062e56c7641","tid":1667984,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa70c81194d4dce0d0648b633a3567b3c7a15e5","tid":1667984,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"太夜開po冇人睇<br />\nP牌幫你唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:03:58.000Z","msg":"都多謝你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"日頭再推過啦"},{"pid":"af26df86fbae42f700d1219dc7b27529eadac502","tid":1667984,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"有冇專門對PoPo既文宣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}